[173.150372, "o", "\u001b[1;32minfo:\u001b[0m Creating a Ruyi virtual environment at \u001b[32mvenv-llvm-ruyisdk-riscv-book\u001b[0m...\r\n"]
[184.497164, "o", "\u001b[1;32minfo:\u001b[0m The virtual environment is now created."]
[184.521038, "o", "\r\n\r\nYou may activate it by sourcing the appropriate activation script in the\r\n\u001b[32mbin\u001b[0m directory, and deactivate by invoking `ruyi-deactivate`.\r\n\r\nA fresh sysroot/prefix is also provisioned in the virtual environment.\r\nIt is available at the following path:\r\n\r\n    \u001b[32m/home/debian/venv-llvm-ruyisdk-riscv-book/sysroot\u001b[0m\r\n\r\nThe virtual environment also comes with ready-made CMake toolchain file\r\nand Meson cross file. Check the virtual environment root for those;\r\ncomments in the files contain usage instructions.\r\n\r\n"]
